question: Character ask for Crowley?
answer:
SEND ME A CHARACTER & I’LL ANSWER THE FOLLOWING ABOUT THEM!

A.J. Crowley

general opinion: fall in a hole and die | don’t like them | eh | they’re fine I guess | like them! | love them | actual love of my life

hotness level: get away from me | meh | neutral | theoretically hot but not my type | pretty hot | gorgeous! | 10/10 would bang

hogwarts house: gryffindor | slytherin | ravenclaw | hufflepuff

best quality: Oh, it’s the love, babey. Crowley loves SO BIG AND SO HARD. He loves plants, he loves his car, he loves his sunglasses and his hair and his sexy clothes, he loves Aziraphale, he loves stupid restaurants with dumbass menus that serve like, a fragment of a dish on a ceiling tile and calls it gourmet, he loves Golden Girls, he loves classical music and he loves blue skies and birds and he loves, and he loves, and he loves!

And the funny thing is that he hides it. He hides it, because he’s not to supposed to be so full of love, and he must be doing it wrong anyway, and it makes him feel vulnerable when people point it out, but it bursts out of him like sunshine and bathes everything he so much as looks at! 

worst quality: His tendency to run away from things, I think. Whether physically throwing himself across the world, or just hiding in his bed for decades on end, his solution to big scary things is basically to coil up and put his hands over his eyes, and like. that’s… that’s not a solution, Anthony. That doesn’t fix anything. I know you’ve got the Anxiety but. Honey, no. 

ship them with: Aziraphale!!!

brotp them with: Also Aziraphale. I also REALLY love Crowley & Drumknott in the crossovers, and I have the BIGGEST respect for Crowley teaming up with himbos like Bertie Wooster. 

needs to stay away from: Work. 

misc. thoughts: I love Crowley so, so much. I just die over like… how much of a dick he is, but how INEFFECTUAL so much of his dickishness is. He doesn’t want to really hurt people and fuck them up - he’s a prankster. He’s a chaotic little beast. He likes to inconvenience people and irritate them and fuck them up, and that’s the most he likes to do. What a bastard! Love him!

blog.title: L'Echappée Belle d' Ygraïn
blog.description:
" Elle voulait une vie d'aventures, une vie folle, une vie plus grande qu'elle.Et l'on disait tout autour d'elle : [Ygraïn] rêve". Timothée de Fombelle, Victoria rêve

Je ne sais pas dessiner, les artworks que vous verrez ici ne sont pas les miens. Mais vous trouverez toujours un lien vers une gallerie de leurs auteurs. Personnellement, je ne fais que des montages (wallpaper, digiscrap, bannière ...) à partir de captures d'écran (screencap).. Ce tumblr est ma gallerie de rêves éphémères, mon échappée belle où je viens me ressourcer, me changer les idées, trouver un support à mes rêveries grâce aux fabuleux arts de d'autres artistes. .
Pour me contacter, en cas de problème: ygrain@gmail.com

Sinon: mon blog de lecture est: https://les-lectures-d-ygrain.tumblr.com/

title: The Rule
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2Xa3EK9

by MandalaRose

“I don’t know,” Charlie says guiltily, “I feel kind of bad. I didn’t mean for Mr. Winchester and Mr. Novak to get stuck late at work cleaning up our prank. They’re good guys. I mean, they’re the co-sponsors of the GSA!”
“Yeah, but don’t you see Charles,” Jo cuts in excitedly, “this could be our chance to finally figure out if those two idiots are actually banging yet!”
“Winvak!” Charlie squeals.

When a senior prank turns into Charlie’s two favorite teachers spending an evening stuck late at work together, she and her two best friends find themselves drawn yet again into their never ending, “are they or aren’t they,” debate. Will they finally learn if openly gay English teacher, Castiel Novak, is actually dating the staff’s charming and seemingly-straight playboy? And if tried-and-true ladies’ man, Dean Winchester, can find himself lusting after his dreamy male coworker, does that mean there’s a chance for Charlie’s hopeless crush on her straight best friend, Jo?
